title: Israeli troops kill at least seven on Gaza border
text:
Israeli troops kill at least seven on Gaza border Friday, April 06, 2018 - 01:43 
Israeli troops have fired on Palestinian protesters at the Gaza border, killing at least seven and wounding more than 150. It brought to 27 the number of Palestinians killed during a week of violence.
